  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    High-Quality Material  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">You’re obviously looking for the highest quality material on your LG G5 skin. Want to know what the difference is between the materials used on ACellShop LG G5 skins and materials used by our competitors? It’s quite simple: only ACellShop uses authentic, true-textured 3M vinyl on every single product we make, including every LG G5 skin. What this means is that when you take off your LG G5 wrap, there’s no need to fear that it’ll leave any adhesive residue on your device. It’s not imitation knockoff vinyl… only the highest grade 3M material on the planet. Furthermore, there’s a couple of LG G5 skins that are only available in our shop, made possible through our massive buying power with 3M. ACellShop LG G5 skins: quality materials, simple installation, precision fit. Our experience and use of only the best materials available gives you peace of mind and confidence in our bold claims.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/quality.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
