  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Unrivaled Precision  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">Precision is a term we take very seriously at dbrand. If you’re in search of the best LG G5 skin on the planet, you’ve come to the right place. Take a look at the photos above and you’ll see that our reputation for the most precise fit on earth is no joke. In order to achieve such a precise fit, we measure each of the cutouts on our LG G5 skins over a thousand times at our Toronto HQ until the LG G5 skins we prototype fit flawlessly on your device. Our LG G5 wraps are created with purpose: they add texture, grip, and factory-fitted customization, all without adding bulk. It genuinely isn’t possible to find a higher quality, more precise LG G5 wrap than the one you’ll find here at dbrand.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/precision.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--g5-variety taxonomy-term--device-features--variety">
